The God of Wealth 🧧.The Zhao Grandmaster is worshipped as the God of Wealth because he was known for his wisdom in financial matters and his generosity towards others.Many businesspeople worship Zhao Gongming to remind themselves to conduct their business honestly & ethically  and to seek wealth through righteous means.Wealth is not something that can be obtained by everyone  but only by those who follow the right path and practice virtuous deeds.
